{"tid":2443040,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"SIM卡實名制快諮詢完　涉\"嚴重罪行\"當局可繞過法庭取得登記資料","createTime":"2021-03-11T20:53:12.000Z","updateTime":"2021-03-12T00:42:44.000Z","uid":261647,"like":4,"dislike":16,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"6e990fc8ed8818f589d2a59312714f41048ea96d","tid":2443040,"uid":261647,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-11T20:53:12.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20210311/XAU5MJYRDJGQDPSL2COU3AQQLU/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20210311%2FXAU5MJYRDJGQDPSL2COU3AQQLU%2F&d=RGPktlJYpqjIeXpZRAkgwwDrJ99PsHpDQ3gYSBhgLgU%3D&h=5d65cfd6\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20210311%2FXAU5MJYRDJGQDPSL2COU3AQQLU%2F&h=1196c3bb\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20210311/XAU5MJYRDJGQDPSL2COU3AQQLU/</a><br />\n<br />\n被質疑是監控手段的SIM卡實名制，公眾諮詢將於下周六（20日）結束，當局昨向立法會提交文件，明文講述何謂毋須法庭手令、要求電訊商提供電話卡登記紀錄的「迫切或緊急理由」，包括需調查將發生的「嚴重罪案」。所謂「嚴重罪案」，即最高刑罰包括罰款不少於100萬元或監禁不少於3年的罪行。"},{"pid":"49898f3401f4bb57459c1b1bf68333161b3c6ece","tid":2443040,"uid":254383,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-11T22:57:49.000Z","msg":"偷呀婆底褲都算嚴重"},{"pid":"e970965b98b2c2ab58cd684b84bd2cb9031ff494","tid":2443040,"uid":259520,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-11T23:07:47.000Z","msg":"唱首歌都可以話告你五年."},{"pid":"b553c277b922e0b6d0176b7446b81917e6b1c989","tid":2443040,"uid":43062,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-11T23:10:57.000Z","msg":"咨詢完照做<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3ab48475599f354ec3db1d54a9d3ea537a0520e8","tid":2443040,"uid":7125,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-11T23:12:07.000Z","msg":"嚴重罪行=搧動對政府/國家仇恨=國安法<br />\n<br />\n而家係佢打你香港人 你鬧佢都唔得 要笑<img src=\"/assets